  /*
   Simplify factorials
  
  The following script
  
  	F(n,k) = k binomial(n,k)
  	(F(n,k) + F(n,k-1)) / F(n+1,k)
  
  generates
  
         k! n!             n! (1 - k + n)!              k! n!
   -------------------- + -------------------- - ----------------------
   (-1 + k)! (1 + n)!     (1 + n)! (-k + n)!     k (-1 + k)! (1 + n)!
  
  Simplify each term to get
  
     k       1 - k + n       1
  ------- + ----------- - -------
   1 + n       1 + n       1 + n
  
  Then simplify the sum to get
  
     n
  -------
   1 + n
   */

